{"tid":1125163,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"尋找細個睇過既電影 （跪求）","createTime":"2019-04-25T13:42:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-25T15:19:47.000Z","uid":170124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"2aec9289dc43f76896a2c1f03d17b4143f8dcb99","tid":1125163,"uid":170124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T13:42:42.000Z","msg":"細個睇過一套電影，好深刻但唔記得左戲名<br />\n想睇返<br />\n外國電影黎既，真人Mix 卡通片<br />\n<br />\n故事大概講<br />\n一班卡通片既人住係節目入面有個世界<br />\n主角住山邊既小屋<br />\n唔知點既出左黎現實世界（好似電台就執立）<br />\n好似有三個角色係主角team 係電視走出黎<br />\n另外有班壞人都走左出黎，壞人Boss 好似女人黎<br />\n<br />\n無啦啦唔知點解主角Team 犯法去左法院<br />\n法官細個有睇過主角Team 既卡通<br />\n話主角Team 係虛擬世界走出黎，法律管唔到<br />\n判無罪<br />\n<br />\n無啦啦唔知點解，係巴黎鐵塔有個密室<br />\n開左機關，巴黎鐵塔有支火箭送主角Team 去其他地方<br />\n<br />\nEnding 好似男主角（卡通人黎）踩左封Email 係網絡世界遊走<br />\n<br />\nSorry for 1999<br />\n希望有人可以解答到我既問題，搵左好都搵唔返！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29b54c74adde8da23c44998b925fc823e5ea54e8","tid":1125163,"uid":170124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T13:44:25.000Z","msg":"推推推"},{"pid":"c6de8164b5bc7410eecc720c33226dabb52ab76c","tid":1125163,"uid":167330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T13:48:40.000Z","msg":"係咪有隻兔仔？"},{"pid":"54a2bf89db2c6fa7c80533fa922451b8307b0982","tid":1125163,"uid":170124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c6de8164b5bc7410eecc720c33226dabb52ab76c","tid":1125163,"uid":167330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T13:48:40.000Z","msg":"係咪有隻兔仔？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T13:49:37.000Z","msg":"好似有呀！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00eaeff8792486a018ba1e6483f88f0e79a65ae0","tid":1125163,"uid":170124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"54a2bf89db2c6fa7c80533fa922451b8307b0982","tid":1125163,"uid":170124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c6de8164b5bc7410eecc720c33226dabb52ab76c","tid":1125163,"uid":167330,"l